@{
    ViewBag.Title = "UserAccount";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/LayoutUsers.cshtml";
}

<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 1500px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">

    <h2 style="font-size: 32px; color: #333; margin-bottom: 20px;">Hi, User</h2>

    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666;">
        Welcome to your user account. Here, you have access to all the tools and features necessary to explore our toy store. From browsing products to managing your orders, everything is designed to provide you with a seamless shopping experience. Feel free to navigate through the various sections and make the most out of your user privileges.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;">
        In addition to exploring our wide range of products, you can also manage your profile, update your preferences, and track your order history. Our goal is to provide you with a user-friendly platform that allows you to find the perfect toys for yourself or your loved ones.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;">
        The user account interface is designed to be intuitive and easy to navigate. Whether you're searching for a specific item, exploring new arrivals, or checking out our special offers, you'll find everything you need to make informed decisions and enjoy a hassle-free shopping experience.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;">
        As you explore your user account, don't hesitate to reach out to our customer support team if you have any questions or need assistance. We're here to help you every step of the way and ensure that your shopping experience exceeds your expectations.
    </p>

</div>
